lyrics:
[verse]
I've been searching for my true reflection
Caught between the lines of reality and perception
Breaking free from the chains, finding my way through
A transgender man, I'm embracing what is true

[chorus]
I'm breaking down these walls, I won't hide anymore
I'll rise above the judgment, breaking stereotypes for sure
This is my journey, my story to unfold
In this pop punk anthem, I'll break the mold
